<Content>We'll Be Back Spent 4 nights here with another couple for our annual city-break together. Need much longer to see the best of Berlin, so we'll be back. Well placed in old Western part, just off Ku'damm, and close to S-Bahn and access to other parts of Berlin, Schoenefeld and Potsdam. Access by the hall and 30s-style lift to the 4th floor is a taster of what's to come. Chic rooms in art nouveau style were very comfortable. BB only, but friendly owners very knowledgeable on the many good local restaurants within minutes' walk, equally helpful on what to do come rain or shine. Honesty bar, well stocked with good but inexpensive German beer and wine. Being BB, no lounge area but that would really have been a bonus. Excellent value. 
